Qbo_face_recognition
====================

A package for face reco learning, and recognizing

faces pics are located in data rep.

for ros indigo / catkinized

SOME MODS WOULD PERHAPS BE NECESSARY !!!

____________________________________________________________________________
+++  need qbo_talk (espeak+mbrola) +++

+++  need qbo_listen (you can simulate listen words with terminal command :

  rostopic pub -1 /listened std_msgs/String "alpha x-ray echo lima fini"

           robot will construct name : axel , and will start learning
____________________________________________________________________________

for recognition :
	rosrun  face_recognition qbo_face_analysis.py

for face learning :
	rosrun  face_recognition qbo_face_learning.py

